Network security

IP tables: 
  - sudo apt install  iptables
  - sudo iptables -L 
  - allow or deny packets
  - rules are based on the order -> top to bottom
   =================================================
   Chain input
    - > Accept
    - > Drop 
    - > Accept
   Chain forward
    Target 
   Chain output
   - > Accept
   - > Accept
   - > Drop

   iptables -A 
   iptables -I
   iptables -D